heading: Plucked instrument music (Plucked instruments (2)).
general-note: Here are entered collections and individual works for two unspecified plucked instruments and collections for various combinations of two plucked instruments. Individual works for two specified plucked instruments, and collections for the same combination, are entered under headings such as. Harp music (Harps (2)); Appalachian dulcimer and guitar music;. etc..
